snippet.textDisplay:
I'm an italian girl living in Italy and I've been watching your videos for almost 6 years now. I used to follow you on Buzzfeed and then, as your were launching your channel, I decided to follow you on this new adventure as well. I always have a nice time watching your videos, and here's something you may not know: they help foreigners learn the language and know more about the American culture. I've actually never been to the u.s and yet I feel like I know lot of things about this country, all thanks to you. You eased me into your culture in a way no teacher could have possibly done, and the funny thing is I am a teacher, so I know what I am talking about. Thank you so much for keeping me updated with all the slang, the habits and the crazy trends. You make me wanna come visit and learn more.
I wish you the best, and if you ever come to Italy, let us know!
Lucia
